# {{ .projectName }}

Grafana Loki log aggregation with Promtail and Grafana.

## Quick Start

    cp .env.example .env
    docker compose up -d

## Access

* Loki API: http://localhost:{{ .lokiPort }}
* Grafana: http://localhost:{{ .grafanaPort }}

Add the Loki datasource in Grafana using the URL http://loki:3100.
Promtail automatically collects logs from all running Docker containers.
